# Slsa Verifier

A lightweight verification tool for validating signed artifacts and provenance generated by CI pipelines.

## Usage

export COSIGN_CERTIFICATE_IDENTITY="your workflow identity"

./scripts/verify_attestation.sh dist/*.whl
